import React from 'react'
import {Container ,Content ,Title ,Reck ,Img1,Img2 ,Img3 ,Img4 ,Co} from './style'
import sel1 from '../../Rasim/sel1.png'
import sel2 from '../../Rasim/sel2.png'
import sel3 from '../../Rasim/sel3.png'
import sel4 from '../../Rasim/sel4.png'
const Testimonial = () => {
    return (
       <Container>

          <Content>
              <Title>Testimonial</Title>
          </Content>
            
          <Reck>
              <Img1  src={sel1}/>
              <Img2  src={sel2}/>
              <Img3  src={sel3}/>
              <Img4  src={sel4}/>
          </Reck>

           <Company>
           
           </Company>
       </Container>
    )
}

export default Testimonial
